org.sureassert.uc.annotation

Annotation Type NoAutoRun


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=TYPE)
public @interface NoAutoRun
    Prevents Sureassert UC running any JUnit tests on the annotated class automatically.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
